snippet.title: Stray Souls - Exclusive Official Trailer | Black Summer 2023
snippet.description: Get another look at dreadful enemies, locations, and more from Stray Souls in this latest trailer for the upcoming third-person action horror game. Stray Souls will be available in Halloween 2023 on Xbox One, Xbox Series X/S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and PC.
